                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="about-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
                                <h4>Comfortable</h4>
                                <p>Ethio Homes provides a comfortable real estate experience with its intuitive interface, extensive property listings, and secure online tools. Easily browse, negotiate, and finalize transactions all in one place, ensuring a stress-free process for buyers, sellers, and tenants.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <i class="fas fa-bullhorn"></i>
                                <h4>Efficiency</h4>
                                <p>Ethio Homes enhances efficiency in real estate transactions with its streamlined processes. From listing properties to finalizing agreements, our platform reduces time and effort, making the buying, selling, and renting experience faster and more straightforward for all users.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i>
                                <h4>Distribution</h4>
                                <p>Ethio Homes connects buyers, sellers, and renters from different locations, providing extensive reach and visibility for all properties. This comprehensive network facilitates efficient and effective real estate transactions nationwide.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <i class="fas fa-id-card-alt"></i>
                                <h4>Transparency</h4>
                                <p>Prioritizes transparency in all interactions. Detailed property descriptions, clear pricing information, and secure online agreements ensure that buyers, sellers, and tenants have all the information they need to make informed decisions confidently.</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
